Story: Appointment creation
As an user
I want to add a new appointment in my calendar
So that I can better organize my time

Scenario: Successful appointment creation
Given I log in as user1
When I create an appointment "Préparer les slides" tomorrow between 11:00 and 12:30
Then I should be redirected to my agenda
And I should see an event "Préparer les slides" in my agenda
And I should be informed that the event has been inserted